{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Kv6oGroFayyzQyS5Aqiidb","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $872.21\n     4→Total API calls: 6354\n     5→Average cost per story: $4.10 (158 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 339,588,803 | $1.50/MTok | $509.38 | 58% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 12,094,864 | $18.75/MTok | $226.78 | 26% |\n    13→| Output | 1,810,975 | $75/MTok | $135.82 | 16% |\n    14→| Input | 14,886 | $15/MTok | $0.22 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 3734 | $466.24 | 53.5% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 874 | $192.87 | 22.1% |\n    22→| retro | 751 | $102.84 | 11.8% |\n    23→| code-review | 376 | $43.15 | 4.9% |\n    24→| create-story | 348 | $37.05 | 4.2% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 3.4% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2343 | $288.35 | 33.1% |\n    32→| Read | 1333 | $184.72 | 21.2% |\n    33→| Edit | 998 | $129.10 | 14.8% |\n    34→| Agent | 610 | $79.64 | 9.1% |\n    35→| Skill | 215 | $74.14 | 8.5% |\n    36→| Grep | 450 | $51.08 | 5.9% |\n    37→| Write | 155 | $27.61 | 3.2% |\n    38→| Glob | 107 | $18.82 | 2.2% |\n    39→| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 1.7% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.4% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 1122 | $224.38 | 25.7% |\n    47→| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 648 | $78.78 | 9.0% |\n    48→| 1-1-foo | 198 | $24.35 | 2.8% |\n    49→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 2.7% |\n    50→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice