r today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"abb1b85b6858e2404","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md`.\n\n**Summary of findings:**\n\n- **Session 32 was a cleanup session.** Stories 16-7 and 16-8 were already implemented and verified in session 31 but their status wasn't committed before session end. This session re-verified proofs, confirmed 321/321 tests at 96.85% coverage, and marked both done. Epic 16 and the full sprint (74/74 stories) are now complete.\n\n- **Cumulative cost: $872.21** (+$155.36 since last retro). Verification is 53.5% of total spend. The \"unknown\" bucket remains at $224.38 (25.7%) unattributed.\n\n- **Key waste sources:** Ralph state corruption (~$150-250 over 35+ sessions), the unattributed \"unknown\" bucket, redundant `npm test` runs in subagents, and this session itself ($10-20) which existed only to fix the status gap.\n\n- **Top action items:** Fix Ralph state corruption (compare-and-swap), add sprint-complete exit condition, make verification-to-done transitions atomic with commit."}],"totalDurationMs":93684,"totalTokens":28736,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2788,"cache_read_input_tokens":25645,"output_tokens":302,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2788},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
